flowchart TD
    A(start)
    B[Set player and enemy characters health to 100%]
    C[Player and enemy take turns attacking each other]
    D{Is player's health <= 0?}
    E[Player loses]
    F{Is enemy's health <= 0?}
    G[Player wins]
    H[Play again?]
    I[Restart game]
    J(End game)

    A --> B
    B --> C
    C --> D
    D -- Yes --> E
    D -- No --> F
    F -- Yes --> G
    F -- No --> C
    E --> H
    G --> H
    H -- Yes --> I
    H -- No --> J
    I --> B
   